Mas. . .

754
01:00:09,487 --> 01:00:10,977
. . .eu a amo.

755
01:00:11,055 --> 01:00:13,080
Se realmente a ama. . .

756
01:00:13,991 --> 01:00:15,982
. . .você a deixará.

757
01:00:20,398 --> 01:00:23,060
- Shrek?
- Señor!

758
01:00:23,167 --> 01:00:26,159
